show.title: The Final Badla
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/t2XvUY
show.description: Final Badla tells the story of a single mother who returns to her family home for her father's birthday, where old criticisms about her single motherhood and life choices immediately resurface. Despite raising three accomplished sons on her own, she faces renewed judgment and hostility from relatives. Through courage and determination, she stands up to the toxic family dynamics and discovers her own pathway to fulfillment and joy.
